{"meta":{"title":"与造物游","subtitle":"流行坎止一虚舟","description":"","author":"Brosharp","url":"http://yoursite.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"All tags","date":"2020-07-08T06:21:27.382Z","updated":"2020-07-08T06:21:27.382Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"All tags","date":"2020-07-08T06:10:32.559Z","updated":"2020-07-08T06:10:32.559Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"杂书过眼录（六月）","slug":"杂书过眼录（六月）","date":"2020-07-06T08:41:57.015Z","updated":"2020-07-08T08:22:39.934Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/07/06/杂书过眼录（六月）/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/07/06/%E6%9D%82%E4%B9%A6%E8%BF%87%E7%9C%BC%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%89/","excerpt":"","text":"《印度对华战争》 [澳]内维尔·马克斯韦尔《虎妈战歌》蔡美儿《高手:精英的见识和我们的时代》万维钢《为奴十二年》Solomon Northup《坚毅》Angela Duckworth《茅海建作品集》套装共5册，因为《天朝的崩溃》早年看过，所以翻了翻《近代的尺度:两次鸦片战争军事与外交》、《从甲午到戊戌：康有为《我史》鉴注》、《戊戌变法史事考初集 》、《戊戌变法史事考二集》。","categories":[{"name":"浮生记","slug":"浮生记","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/%E6%B5%AE%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%B0/"}],"tags":[{"name":"阅读史","slug":"阅读史","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%B2/"}]},{"title":"“听蝼蛄叫还不种庄稼了？”","slug":"“听蝼蛄叫还不种庄稼了？”","date":"2020-07-06T08:13:46.912Z","updated":"2020-07-08T08:26:53.581Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/07/06/“听蝼蛄叫还不种庄稼了？”/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/07/06/%E2%80%9C%E5%90%AC%E8%9D%BC%E8%9B%84%E5%8F%AB%E8%BF%98%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%8D%E5%BA%84%E7%A8%BC%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F%E2%80%9D/","excerpt":"","text":"There were many mole crickets and we could hear them chirp at night. There was a popular expression among us: “Don’t stop planting wheat just because mole crickets chirp,” which means you should not let little problems or risks prevent you from doing what is necessary. I still follow such wisdom today. Weijian Shan Out of the Gobi 去年初秋翻到这一段时心中忽有所悟，暗下决心要完成一桩拖了很久的事情，到本月初终于告成。聊记一笔。","categories":[{"name":"浮生记","slug":"浮生记","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/%E6%B5%AE%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%B0/"}],"tags":[{"name":"人生智慧","slug":"人生智慧","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/"},{"name":"书摘","slug":"书摘","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/%E4%B9%A6%E6%91%98/"}]},{"title":"望断白云","slug":"望断白云","date":"2020-05-06T05:43:41.459Z","updated":"2020-07-08T08:20:13.370Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/05/06/望断白云/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/05/06/%E6%9C%9B%E6%96%AD%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%91/","excerpt":"","text":"因无人接送不得不上晚托班的日子里，小朋友到家后没事就搬张小凳子站在北窗前引领而望，我起初还以为她牢记我平日教导，看书作业半小时后便举目远眺放松眼睫肌。直到有一天她打电话给奶奶，说每次想奶奶的时候就望望天上的云，看久了好像云彩中变幻出了奶奶的模样，直接把奶奶说哽咽了。昔年狄仁杰受阎立本举荐，到太原任职法曹参军，其父母远在河阳（今河南孟县），一日『登太行山，南望见白云孤飞，谓左右曰：“吾亲所居，在此云下。”瞻望伫立久之，云移乃行。”』遂有“白云亲舍”之典。小朋友天真烂漫，说啥都是发自肺腑，迥出天机。 (2015-7-6)","categories":[{"name":"浮生记","slug":"浮生记","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/%E6%B5%AE%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%B0/"}],"tags":[{"name":"童言趣语","slug":"童言趣语","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/%E7%AB%A5%E8%A8%80%E8%B6%A3%E8%AF%AD/"}]},{"title":"没有什么可以阻挡","slug":"没有什么可以阻挡","date":"2020-04-30T06:44:41.822Z","updated":"2020-07-08T08:02:54.708Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/04/30/没有什么可以阻挡/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/04/30/%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%BB%E6%8C%A1/","excerpt":"","text":"我对开学的向往……","categories":[{"name":"浮生记","slug":"浮生记","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/%E6%B5%AE%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%B0/"}],"tags":[{"name":"新冠","slug":"新冠","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0/"}]},{"title":"闲书过眼录——趣味生活简史","slug":"闲书过眼录——趣味生活简史","date":"2020-04-30T06:04:29.099Z","updated":"2020-07-08T08:21:16.406Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/04/30/闲书过眼录——趣味生活简史/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/04/30/%E9%97%B2%E4%B9%A6%E8%BF%87%E7%9C%BC%E5%BD%95%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%AE%80%E5%8F%B2/","excerpt":""